sequenceDiagram
    participant Config
    participant API
    participant Parser as Dedicated C-Struct Parser
    participant Meta
    participant Time
    participant Env
    participant Handoff

    Config->>Config: Resolve layout + parser
    API->>Parser: C-style struct buffer
    Parser->>Parser: Read explicit offsets/sizes
    Parser-->>Env: Parsed C-struct field view
    Meta-->>Env: Prepared metadata
    Time-->>Env: Stabilized timestamp
    Env->>Handoff: Ready exposure
